# EXTRACTED KNOWLEDGE BASE

## [1] Understand: AI, AGI, ASI
- AGI (Artificial General Intelligence): AI that can perform any intellectual task a human can.
- ASI (Artificial Superintelligence): AI that surpasses human intelligence across all fields.
- Metrics: Google DeepMind's Levels of AGI (Emergent, Competent, Expert, Virtuoso, Superhuman).

## [2] Understand: Collective Intelligence
- Focuses on Multi-Agent Systems (MAS) and Swarm Intelligence.
- Importance of Human-AI collaboration and Emergent Intelligence.

## [3] Build: Frameworks & Agents
- Tools like AutoGPT, BabyAGI, and specialized agent frameworks (MetaGPT, ChatDev).
- Focus on automation, coding agents, and local agent stacks.

## [4] Infrastructure
- Covers RAG, Vector DBs, Fine-tuning (LoRA), and Deployment.
- Distributed training and compute hardware (custom silicon).

## [5] Safety & Governance
- Focus on Alignment, Interpretability, and Planetary-Scale challenges.
- Agent safety and control mechanisms.

## [6] Research & Learn
